TruTech Tools: Thanks for reaching out, and I'm sorry to hear that! Are you referring to the order that was placed on 02/09? If so, please note that orders are processed 7 days a week and most orders received before 3:00 pm EST will ship the same day, provided the product ordered is in stock. After your order is shipped, we will forward the tracking number so you can follow your package which will update with an ETA on delivery. At this time we don't ship internationally.

Please let me know how I can assist you further today, I'm just a text away!
